  "body": "### What is wrong?\r\nSet sharding protocol constants and configuration\r\n\r\n### How can it be fixed\r\n\r\n1. Protocol constants are listed here: https://github.com/ethereum/sharding/blob/develop/docs/doc.md#constants\r\n  Find an appropriate place to set these parameters.\r\n\r\n2. Node configuration\r\n    * Related issue: Related to https://github.com/ethereum/py-evm/issues/198\r\n    * Sharding only configuration: (Ref: https://github.com/ethereum/sharding/blob/develop/docs/doc.md#client-logic)\r\n        * `validator_address`: \"0x...\" OR null\r\n        * `watching`: [list of shard IDs]\r\n    * DB setting (TBD): one DB for each shard\r\n\r\nWe can start `1. Protocol constants` now and leave `2. Node configuration` after #198 is solved or after we start `ShardManager` implementation.\r\n\r\n",
